{"tid":2406962,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"屌，新年真係咪撚再一開口就恭喜發財","createTime":"2021-02-13T15:17:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T18:28:14.000Z","uid":109748,"like":183,"dislike":338,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"1623faa36118684028df667c34d6af73e3c2f5c9","tid":2406962,"uid":109748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T15:17:50.000Z","msg":"首先，呢四隻字本身就唔make sense，個人未發達你恭喜佢做乜9，係咪全港呢幾日一齊發達？<br />\n<br />\n另外，有好多有意思嘅恭賀説話，想人有成長有進步嘅可以講萬事如意心想事成，想人健康咪身體健康龍馬精神，想人擺脫現狀咪萬象更新否極泰來，就算講打工做生意都有步步高升大展鴻圖。<br />\n<br />\n最後，我屌你老母，新年個個開口埋口錢錢錢，懷疑呢個世界得我地華人新年呢個節日咁撚屎檜，用現金當禮物已經痴撚線，個個淨係care邊個親戚封幾錢，個節日已經冇咩內涵，就好心係恭賀説話到諗多少少。"},{"pid":"e91ee9b246b1d712322a7eafe1c668f5398376b6","tid":2406962,"uid":38540,"like":350,"dislike":14,"score":336,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T15:18:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://memes.tw/meme/9c8334b44e9f3bfbeefc05a5b162aa1e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmemes.tw%2Fmeme%2F9c8334b44e9f3bfbeefc05a5b162aa1e.png&h=edf347b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b0dbf8d12f7b0401e3451a4abc57ae6e4599344f","tid":2406962,"uid":55458,"like":84,"dislike":6,"score":78,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T15:20:04.000Z","msg":"個個發財啲錢會貶值<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n社會點都要有九成奴隸先可以運作到"},{"pid":"db2b32957a9fc10c808dad4aa95e57b9d491d2ac","tid":2406962,"uid":80691,"like":2,"dislike":28,"score":-26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T15:20:14.000Z","msg":"牛轉乾坤"},{"pid":"661c1006843141593ac3b4f0e5dfcdea97ff3725","tid":2406962,"uid":391931,"like":24,"dislike":6,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T15:22:45.000Z","msg":"未來式啊柒頭<br />\n呢啲基層圍爐有嘅習俗<br />\n邊個基層唔望發達姐<br />\n<br />\n所以話你都唔識嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"930fac0d1ea685258c48eb3e4dfdc04874a89b3a","tid":2406962,"uid":2419,"like":54,"dislike":6,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T15:24:20.000Z","msg":"大家咁話"},{"pid":"556de5b1f2c7154a827cf862bb9358907eade807","tid":2406962,